<p><i><b>The Pilgrim's Progress from This World to That Which Is to Come</b></i> by <a href="/wiki/John_Bunyan" title="John Bunyan">John Bunyan</a> (published February, 1678) is a <a href="/wiki/Christian" title="Christian">Christian</a> <a href="/wiki/Allegory" title="Allegory">allegory</a>. It is regarded as one of the most significant works of <a href="/wiki/English_literature" title="English literature">English literature</a>, has been translated into more than 200 languages, and has never been out of print.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
